chatWelcomeView.welcomeViewContent:
You have access to [GitHub Copilot](command:extension.open?%5B%22github.copilot%22%5D), an AI-powered coding assistant, as a part of the Microsoft organization.
 Getting started with Copilot is easy - simply install the Copilot extension. [Learn more](https://aka.ms/copilot-overview)
